The paper proposes an algorithm for joint channel estimation and data detection in massive MIMO wireless systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
